      • CRYPTO_KEY_V2

        static final String CRYPTO_KEY_V2
        Encrypted symmetric key header that is used in the Authenticated Encryption (AE) cryptographic module. Older versions of COS encryption client with encryption-only capability would not be able to recognize this AE key, and therefore will be prevented from mistakenly decrypting ciphertext in AE format.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
